{"tid":2162500,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"老豆住醫院 醫極都醫唔好","createTime":"2020-08-18T07:09:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-22T02:00:31.000Z","uid":304029,"like":1,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"d4220f69435076cfbe08336eb273feb20f0a104a","tid":2162500,"uid":304029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T07:09:05.000Z","msg":"起初因爲懷疑中風入左醫院<br />\n住院期間不斷發燒，連續燒左幾個星期，到而家都未退到<br />\n醫院不斷俾藥佢食，但食極都冇效，一隻藥唔得換第二隻，到而家仲未醫得到。本身入院之前佢個精神狀況都ok，但而家食藥食到個人開始神智不清，沌沌鄧鄧<br />\n<br />\n屋企人想接佢出院，因為住院以黎佢情況冇好過不突止仲比以前差左，但我覺得就算佢出院都幫唔到佢退燒，但佢繼續住院的確個病情完全冇好轉<br />\n<br />\n到底應該點<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b91d07c391dd9853f1c8aa259e5f13ed87eb9a55","tid":2162500,"uid":127955,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T07:10:00.000Z","msg":"住咩醫院喔"},{"pid":"0cb914c0e97a275f0029afa5e1d31c03574fe32a","tid":2162500,"uid":304029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b91d07c391dd9853f1c8aa259e5f13ed87eb9a55","tid":2162500,"uid":127955,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T07:10:00.000Z","msg":"住咩醫院喔"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T07:10:52.000Z","msg":"公立"},{"pid":"fad2ff27e113be09cd986153359f5c89c1813a60","tid":2162500,"uid":313635,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T07:12:01.000Z","msg":"撞鬼?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c112d66889c45067efac1ec30aa043e1d297c72e","tid":2162500,"uid":653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T07:13:06.000Z","msg":"咁有冇講咩病 肯定係中風？"},{"pid":"dd3418b9cc8f9b9c0b53738f71ffede4ff4f9e24","tid":2162500,"uid":304029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c112d66889c45067efac1ec30aa043e1d297c72e","tid":2162500,"uid":653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T07:13:06.000Z","msg":"咁有冇講咩病 肯定係中風？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T07:15:44.000Z","msg":"係 話驗到一早已經有血管塞左 唔係最近既事<br />\n前幾日就話佢發燒個原因係病毒性腦膜炎 今