"pid":"cb39a618e2220fb9324906d465e8e82f8a4433dc","tid":2162500,"uid":327593,"like":12,"dislike":2,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T07:28:32.000Z","msg":"最撚憎樓主喱種人 嫌三嫌四 包醫好咁款<br />\n拿拿聲轉院去養和啦"},{"pid":"70f8bf17da2dd5f8168617fc68005aed845905d3","tid":2162500,"uid":255644,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T07:29:31.000Z","msg":"其實首先要diagnose腦膜炎應該已經要好多時間<br />\n有病人發燒 首先會幫佢照肺，抽血，同留尿睇下係咪啲common嘅感染<br />\n依啲都做左而仲係發燒嘅話先會考慮去做lumber puncture 去留脊髓液去種菌<br />\n而TB依隻菌亦都係好難好耐先種到同去醫<br />\n所以要搞咁耐<br />\n亦都點解成日轉藥就係因為應該試過好多種抗生素 因為唔同菌要用唔同抗生素醫<br />\n而家搵到咩菌就好啦<br />\n希望uncle好番啦"},{"pid":"8a62b0e8a2624447a6d30866e08dd6c0b22bcc94","tid":2162500,"uid":304029,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"ba51c37c243f63e6f52f0bf22d32fbfae0deb939","tid":2162500,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T07:23:54.000Z","msg":"中風會發燒嫁咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你假膠定我真心"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T07:33:00.000Z","msg":"冇話係中風所以發燒喎 佢一開始係中風所以入院<br />\n後面咪講到係腦膜炎囉 醫院驗左兩個星期先驗到發燒原因呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82ad5dd6fbf26888143813a36aed8aa70e1f0609","tid":2162500,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T07:35:14.000Z","msg":"咁危險仲出院？一陣有咩事要白車送番院<br />\n<br />\n果幾十分鐘好關鍵<br />\n<br />\n醫院有人睇住"},{"pid":"ab5153b7ca70fcc700f312ac1c30bb1aed26bb13","tid":2162500,"uid":203889,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"dd3418b9cc8f9b9c0b53738f71ffede4ff4f9e24","tid":2162500,"uid":304029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c112d66889c45067efac1ec30aa043e1d297c72e","tid":2162500,"uid":653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T07:13:06.000Z","msg":"咁有冇講咩病 肯定係中風？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T07:15:44.000Z","msg":"係 話驗到一早已經有血管塞左 唔係最近既事<br />\n前幾日就話佢發燒個原因係病毒性腦膜炎 今日打嚟又話係結核性腦膜炎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T07:35:41.000Z","msg":"原來腦膜炎<br />\n唔該乖乖住院"},{"pid":"eaff2c0fb77bb0bf0a072626425fcfbb228fe2d6","tid":2162500,"uid":231443,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T07:36:25.000Z","msg":"樓主你唔好將個重點放係發燒同神志到，腦膜炎一日唔搞掂，啲野都係一路keep住咁。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n時發時唔發係因為有食藥，如果唔食就24小時咁發落去。另外個肝腎功能差，個醫生可能唔敢比啲勁既藥，如果一比左你啊爸可能唔知邊個器官衰竭，咁就更加麻煩<br />\n<br />\n最後入醫院唔會係包醫好🙈"},{"pid":"594a10f577246fddf1d9003844ca833708d7939e","tid":2162500,"uid":180124,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"dfd658ed74621fcf6d972e6c8af957109bab4885","tid":2162500,"uid":304029,"like":1,"dislike":26,"score":-25,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T07:16:35.000Z","msg":"屌你老母點解公立醫院咁撚廢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T07:38:15.000Z","msg":"問林奠啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又要cut cost"},{"pid":"bdc531e0193404460f20601e128993c7235a0588","tid":2162500,"uid":333199,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T07:43:35.000Z","msg":"好似有買醫保,希望第時住院唔洗入公立"},{"pid":"e3fbfbc1fdd86e354846606f7053617590cffff3","tid":2162500,"uid":138818,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8a62b0e8a2624447a6d30866e08dd6c0b22bcc94","tid":2162500,"uid":304029,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"ba51c37c243f63e6f52f0bf22d32fbfae0deb939","tid":2162500,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T07:23:54.000Z","msg":"中風會發燒嫁咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你假膠定我真心"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T07:33:00.000Z","msg":"冇話係中風所以發燒喎 佢一開始係中風所以入院<br />\n後面咪講到係腦膜炎囉 醫院驗左兩個星期先驗到發燒原因呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T07:43:42.000Z","msg":"dama 囉 fever只係sign 大把cause"},{"pid":"02226d84fa7b4eed92d251e99b40c0854d171487","tid":2162500,"uid":250550,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"1cb53a5e09e75f0bf89412363e61e214a88beb49","tid":2162500,"uid":160251,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"dd3418b9cc8f9b9c0b53738f71ffede4ff